  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdGuardHome/tarball/v0.107.73",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdGuardHome/zipball/v0.107.73",
  "body": "We are releasing this hotfix to address a recently discovered critical vulnerability that could allow users to bypass authentication and gain full access to AdGuard Home without valid credentials. We strongly recommend updating your AdGuard Home clients immediately.\r\n\r\n## Acknowledgments\r\n\r\nA special thanks to @mandreko for reporting the vulnerability, our community moderators team and to everyone who filed and inspected issues, added translations, and helped us test this release!\r\n\r\n## Full changelog\r\n\r\nSee also the [v0.107.73 GitHub milestone][ms-v0.107.73].\r\n\r\n### Security\r\n\r\n- Authentication is now applied to requests that have been upgraded from HTTP/2 Cleartext (H2C) requests to public resources.\r\n\r\n  **NOTE:** We thank @mandreko for reporting this security issue.\r\n\r\n[ms-v0.107.73]: https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdGuardHome/milestone/108?closed=1\r\n",
